{"title":"花千骨——仙剑大会","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3946","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仙剑大会就要开始了，十一正忙着安排，这次共N个人，两两对比，糖宝问十一：“十一师兄，十一师兄！按长留的比赛方法，要比几场？怎么比啊”，于是，十一师兄萌化了。<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个数N。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>参见样例和提示</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>8</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>7</p><p>4 2 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<ol style=\"\"><li><p>长留弟子8000，参赛的为2的次方。</p></li><li><p>样例：共<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">7</span></strong></span>场；</p><p>8人分4组，比<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">4</span></strong></span>场；</p><p>胜出的4人分2组，比<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">2</span></strong></span>场；</p><p>胜出的2人分1组，比<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">1</span></strong></span>场；</p></li></ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}